---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import backgroundImage from '../assets/children-hero.jpg';
---

<Layout title="About Us - Otacho Hands of Grace Community Care" description="Learn about Otacho Hands of Grace Community Care's mission in water and sanitation, environmental sustainability, child protection, gender equality, and vocational training in Migori, Kenya.">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <section class="relative bg-black/50 text-white py-24 overflow-hidden">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat"
        style={`background-image: url(${backgroundImage.src});`}
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6 animate-slide-up font-sans">About Us</h1>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-blue-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
          Discover our mission, vision, programs, and the transformative impact we're making in children's lives.
        </p>
        <a href="/donate" class="mt-6 inline-block bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105" aria-label="Support our mission">
          Support Our Mission
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission & Vision -->
    <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-blue-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 animate-slide-up">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3.172 5.172a4 4 0 015.656 0L10 6.343l1.172-1.171a4 4 0 115.656 5.656L10 17.657l-6.828-6.829a4 4 0 010-5.656z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4 font-sans">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
              To empower vulnerable communities in Migori, Kenya through sustainable development initiatives that address water and sanitation challenges, promote environmental sustainability, protect children and families, advance gender equality, support orphans, and create economic opportunities through vocational training and job creation.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M10 12a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z"/>
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M.458 10C1.732 5.943 5.522 3 10 3s8.268 2.943 9.542 7c-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7S1.732 14.057.458 10zM14 10a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4 font-sans">Our Vision</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
              A thriving Migori community where every individual has access to clean water, sustainable livelihoods, quality education, and equal opportunities regardless of gender. We envision empowered communities that are resilient, self-sufficient, and actively contributing to Kenya's development goals.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Story -->
    <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-slide-up">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4 font-sans">Our Story</h2>
            <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600">How it all began</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-12 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              <p class="mb-6">
                Otacho Hands of Grace Community Care was established in Migori, Kenya with a clear vision to address the multifaceted challenges facing vulnerable communities in the region. Recognizing that poverty, lack of clean water, environmental degradation, and limited economic opportunities were interconnected issues, our founders created a comprehensive approach to community development.
              </p>
              <p class="mb-6">
                What began as a small community initiative has evolved into a dynamic Community Based Organization that serves thousands of households across Migori County. Our work spans from drilling boreholes and constructing sanitation facilities to implementing environmental conservation projects, protecting vulnerable children, empowering girls and women, and providing vocational training that leads to sustainable employment.
              </p>
              <p>
                Through partnerships with local communities, government agencies, and international donors, we have successfully implemented programs that not only provide immediate relief but also build long-term resilience. Our success is measured by the number of families with access to clean water, the girls who complete their education, the youth who find meaningful employment, and the communities that become self-sufficient and environmentally conscious.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-8 text-center">
              <a
                href="#impact"
                class="inline-block bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 px-6 sm:px-8 py-3 sm:py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-base sm:text-lg hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105"
                aria-label="Learn more about our impact"
              >
                Learn More About Our Impact
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Programs -->
    <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-blue-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-slide-up">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4 font-sans">What We Do</h2>
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600">Comprehensive programs nurturing every aspect of a child's development</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Programs Grid (3 columns) -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
          <!-- Water and Sanitation Program -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 animate-slide-up">
            <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white w-12 h-12 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1V4zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4 font-sans">Water & Sanitation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
              Providing sustainable access to clean water and proper sanitation facilities to improve health outcomes and quality of life in Migori communities.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700 text-sm sm:text-base">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Borehole Drilling & Maintenance
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700 text-sm sm:text-base">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Latrine Construction
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700 text-sm sm:text-base">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Water Quality Testing
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700 text-sm sm:text-base">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Hygiene Education Programs
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Environmental Sustainability Program -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
            <div class="bg-green-600 text-white w-12 h-12 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.083 9h1.946c.089-1.546.383-2.97.837-4.118A6.004 6.004 0 004.083 9zM10 2a8 8 0 100 16 8 8 0 000-16zm0 2c-.076 0-.232.032-.465.262-.238.234-.497.623-.737 1.182-.389.907-.673 2.142-.766 3.556h3.936c-.093-1.414-.377-2.649-.766-3.556-.24-.56-.5-.948-.737-1.182C10.232 4.032 10.076 4 10 4zm3.971 5c-.089-1.546-.383-2.97-.837-4.118A6.004 6.004 0 0113.917 9h1.946zm-2.003 2H8.032c.093 1.414.377 2.649.766 3.556.24.56.5.948.737 1.182.233.23.389.262.465.262.076 0 .232-.032.465-.262.238-.234.498-.623.737-1.182.389-.907.673-2.142.766-3.556zm1.166 4.118c.454-1.147.748-2.572.837-4.118h1.946a6.004 6.004 0 01-2.783 4.118zm-6.268 0C6.412 13.97 6.118 12.546 6.03 11H4.083a6.004 6.004 0 002.783 4.118z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4 font-sans">Environmental Sustainability</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
              Promoting environmental conservation, sustainable agriculture, and climate resilience to ensure long-term ecological balance and food security.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700 text-sm sm:text-base">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Tree Planting & Reforestation
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700 text-sm sm:text-base">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Sustainable Agriculture Training
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700 text-sm sm:text-base">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Waste Management Programs
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700 text-sm sm:text-base">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Climate Change Adaptation
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Life Skills & Vocational Training Program -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
            <div class="bg-indigo-600 text-white w-12 h-12 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.49 3.17c-.38-1.56-2.6-1.56-2.98 0a1.532 1.532 0 01-2.286.948c-1.372-.836-2.942.734-2.106 2.106.54.886.061 2.042-.947 2.287-1.561.379-1.561 2.6 0 2.978a1.532 1.532 0 01.947 2.287c-.836 1.372.734 2.942 2.106 2.106a1.532 1.532 0 012.287.947c.379 1.561 2.6 1.561 2.978 0a1.533 1.533 0 012.287-.947c1.372.836 2.942-.734 2.106-2.106a1.533 1.533 0 01.947-2.287c1.561-.379 1.561-2.6 0-2.978a1.532 1.532 0 01-.947-2.287c.836-1.372-.734-2.942-2.106-2.106a1.532 1.532 0 01-2.287-.947zM10 13a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4 font-sans">Life Skills & Vocational Training</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
              Practical life skills and vocational training programs that prepare youth for independent living and successful careers through hands-on learning and skill development.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700 text-sm sm:text-base">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Carpentry & Construction Skills
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700 text-sm sm:text-base">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Tailoring & Fashion Design
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700 text-sm sm:text-base">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                ICT & Computer Skills
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700 text-sm sm:text-base">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Entrepreneurship Training
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Additional Programs Grid (4 columns) -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 sm:gap-8 p-6 sm:p-8">
          <!-- Child Protection and Family Welfare -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-blue-100 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 animate-slide-up">
            <div class="bg-red-600 text-white w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 sm:h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3.172 5.172a4 4 0 015.656 0L10 6.343l1.172-1.171a4 4 0 115.656 5.656L10 17.657l-6.828-6.829a4 4 0 010-5.656z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2 font-sans">Child Protection & Family Welfare</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Safeguarding children from abuse, exploitation, and neglect while strengthening family units and providing comprehensive support services.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Gender Equality and Girl Empowerment -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-blue-100 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
            <div class="bg-purple-600 text-white w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 sm:h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2 font-sans">Gender Equality & Girl Empowerment</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Empowering girls and women through education, skills training, and leadership development to achieve gender equality.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Child and Orphan Sponsorship -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-blue-100 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
            <div class="bg-orange-600 text-white w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 sm:h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2 font-sans">Child & Orphan Sponsorship</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Comprehensive sponsorship programs providing education, healthcare, and nutritional support for orphans and vulnerable children.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Vocational Training and Job Creation -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-blue-100 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
            <div class="bg-green-600 text-white w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 sm:h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-6-3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zm-2 4a5 5 0 00-4.546 2.916A5.986 5.986 0 0010 16a5.986 5.986 0 004.546-2.084A5 5 0 0010 11z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2 font-sans">Vocational Training & Job Creation</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Skills development and entrepreneurship training to create sustainable employment opportunities and economic empowerment.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Impact Section -->
    <section id="impact" class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-blue-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-slide-up">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4 font-sans">Our Impact</h2>
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600">Real stories from the lives we've touched</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonials Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
          <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 animate-slide-up">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <img src="/src/assets/img/testimonial-1.jpg" alt="Maria" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover mr-4">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-900 font-sans">Maria</h4>
              </div>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="text-gray-700 italic text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
              "Before coming here, I didn't know what a real family felt like. Now I have hope for my future. The education and love I've received have changed everything for me."
            </blockquote>
          </div>

          <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <img src="/src/assets/img/testimonial-2.jpg" alt="James" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover mr-4">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-900 font-sans">James</h4>
              </div>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="text-gray-700 italic text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
              "Thanks to the vocational training I received, I now have a stable job as a carpenter. The home gave me not just skills, but the confidence to build a better life."
            </blockquote>
